let f = fun x -> (
    let r: {type t; x: t; f: t->t} = x;
    print r.x;
);
####
TypeError: Value is required to be a monomorphic record here:
let f = fun x -> (
    let r: {type t; x: t; f: t->t} = x;
    print r.x;
           ^~  
);
However, that value may be a polymorphic record here:
let f = fun x -> (
    let r: {type t; x: t; f: t->t} = x;
           ^~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~      
    print r.x;
);
Hint: To access fields on a polymorphic record, you need to first bind it as a module. (mod M = ...)
